                        <p class="text-[22px] font-bold" style="color: #1E293B;">si (四声)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-3 px-4" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                        <p class="text-[13px] mb-1" style="color: #16A34A;">释义</p>
                        <p class="text-[16px]" style="color: #374151;">地支第六位（蛇）</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-3 px-4" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                        <p class="text-[13px] mb-1" style="color: #16A34A;">组词</p>
                        <div class="flex justify-center gap-2">
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-[14px]" style="background-color: #F0FDF4; color: #374151;">巳时</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-[14px]" style="background-color: #F0FDF4; color: #374151;">巳蛇</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-[14px]" style="background-color: #F0FDF4; color: #374151;">己巳年</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-2 px-4" style="background-color: #16A34A;">
                        <p class="text-[14px] font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">全部出头</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 底部记忆口诀条 -->
        <div class="h-[60px] flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #E8573A;">
            <p class="text-[16px] font-serif" style="color: #FFFFFF;">
                左不出头是<span class="font-bold text-[18px] mx-1">己</span>自己，
                左边出头是<span class="font-bold text-[18px] mx-1">已</span>已经，
                全都出头是<span class="font-bold text-[18px] mx-1">巳</span>巳蛇
            </p>
